{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove the cap on NI Contributions relief for pension salary sacrifice ",
        "additional_details": "We believe the Government should not disincentivise people from making the right choices to save for their own future and reducing their reliance on the state to fund their retirement.",
        "background": "Reverse proposals to charge National Insurance on salary-sacrificed pension contributions over \u00a32000 to encourage people to save for retirement and reduce reliance on the state pension.",
